                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210912-130-off758 t18210912-130-cd759"></join>, three shirts, value 12 s.; three pair of stockings, value 2 s., and one handkerchief, value 6 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210912-130-victim1401" type="victimName">
